				<text>Contact Federation command.</text>
				<event>
					<text>On the vidscreen appears several Federation and Engi officers, as well as Admiral Tully in the center. "Is that... a triangular ship? What a completely alien design, I've never seen anything like it before... Well, I suppose we need all the help we can get, and judging from the technology your ship holds, you may be just the help we need."</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event load="LAST_STAND_START_2"/>
